tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE booking_schedules (
    schedule_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    venue_id INT,
    event_date DATE,
    event_time TIME,
    performer TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY (venue_id) REFERENCES music_venues(venue_id)
);

CREATE TABLE booking_schedules (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  venue_id INT,
  event_date DATE,
  start_time TIME,
  end_time TIME
);

CREATE TABLE booking_schedules (
    schedule_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    venue_id INT,
    date DATE NOT NULL,
    start_time TIME NOT NULL,
    end_time TIME NOT NULL
);
CREATE TABLE venue (venue_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, venue_name STRING, location STRING)
CREATE TABLE artist (artist_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, artist_name STRING, genre STRING)
CREATE TABLE booking (booking_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, venue_id UUID, artist_id UUID, booking_date DATE, booking_time TIME)
CREATE TABLE event (event_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, venue_id UUID, event_name STRING, event_date DATE)
CREATE TABLE ticket (ticket_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, event_id UUID, ticket_price DECIMAL)
